A sleek cyberpunk cityscape at night with towering holographic server racks and data streams flowing like neon rivers between buildings. In the foreground, a lone developer sits at a floating workstation surrounded by multiple translucent screens displaying code and network pathways. Glowing proxy tunnels connect different sections of the city, visualized as bright teal and magenta energy bridges routing through a central hub. The atmosphere is moody with rain-slicked streets reflecting the electric glow above. Circuit board patterns are subtly embedded in the architecture, and small drones carry packets of light data between structures. The color palette emphasizes deep purples, electric blues, and hot pink accents against dark chrome surfaces.
